---
title: Char Siu Plant-Based Mince & Veggie Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Sesame Seeds
description: Elevate your plant-based dining experience with this veggie-packed stir-fry! Sticky and fragrant, this dish is ready in a blink of
an eye and will satisfy all your stir-fry needs. Fluffy jasmine rice is a must to soak up all that rich sticky sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65a8bd3b553f74890680d1c2-e4030e6a.jpeg
